### Alternative: Stored Procedure Approach

If your organization uses centralized schema provisioning, you can call the provisioning stored procedure instead of running the inline SQL:

```sql
{%- for zone in zone_list %}
{%- for schema in schema_definitions if schema.zone == zone %}
CALL INFRA.UTL_PROVISION.PROVISION_SCHEMA_SP(
  '<database_name>',
  '{{ schema.schema_name | upper }}',
  {{ data_retention_days | default(1) }},
  '{{ schema.purpose }}',
  TRUE
);
{%- endfor %}
{%- endfor %}
```

Contact your platform team to confirm the stored procedure is available in your account.